# Rename to Configuration.storekit and create via Xcode (File > New > StoreKit Configuration File).
# Example product IDs to define inside Xcode's editor:
#   pro.weekly   (auto-renewable, 1 week, with intro free trial)
#   pro.yearly   (auto-renewable, 1 year)
# Then: Scheme > Edit Scheme > Run > Options > StoreKit Configuration > select it.
